* [07aug2007] This is version 0.3. Abstract base classes have been
  removed, simplifying the interface.  Also, static member variables
  have been removed, making it possible to create multiple suffixtree
  objects.
* [17jun2003] This is version 0.2.  A generic and a concrete iterator
  class have been added.  This allows for specific operations on the
  suffixtree.
* [19dec2002] This is version 0.1 (alpha).  Please let me know if you
  have any problems using the package or not.

// end of file: NEWS
